  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Image, Knife, and Gluepot (2019), published by Open Book Publishers. Sustainability & policy relevance (strength 0.6). 6215 downloads \u2014 actief gebruik.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Image, Knife, and Gluepot was published by Open Book Publishers in 2019. Conceptually, the work connects to Fifteenth, Materiality (auditing), Afterlife, Art and Publishing.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">OpenAlex records 6 citations. Citations peaked in 2023 with 3 citing works. Notable citing venues include Exemplaria, Journal of Medieval Iberian Studies and Religions. Inferred role: Sustainability & policy relevance and Scholarly uptake.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">6215 recorded downloads via open-access infrastructure.  SDG alignment: Quality Education.</p>",
